[claude stdout] {"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01K2ALCrDgSyMXJYi2J4eDnj","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The `findFileByLastModifiedDate` view on `projectDocumentService` should list files in a project. The start/end keys likely include the project ID.\n\nHere's a window showing the files in your selected project:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"op\": \"addWindow\",\n  \"id\": \"win-files\",\n  \"title\": \"Files — python_auto_project\",\n  \"size\": \"medium\",\n  \"align\": \"right\",\n  \"content\": {\n    \"type\": \"ListView\",\n    \"id\": \"lv-files\",\n    \"props\": {\"padding\": 12},\n    \"dataSource\": {\n      \"service\": \"projectDocumentService\",\n      \"method\": \"findFileByLastModifiedDate\",\n      \"args\": [[\"b35d8b128969e6578e7b525a656fc4df\", \"0000\"], [\"b35d8b128969e6578e7b525a656fc4df\", \"9999\"], 50]\n    },\n    \"children\": [\n      {\n        \"type\": \"Card\",\n        \"id\": \"fcard-{{item.id}}\",\n        \"props\": {\"elevation\": 2},\n        \"selectedChannel\": \"system.selection.file\",\n        \"selectedMatchKey\": \"fileId\",\n        \"selectedMatchValue\": \"{{item.id}}\",\n        \"selectedProps\": {\"color\": \"#E3F2FD\", \"elevation\": 4},\n        \"actions\": {\n          \"onTap\": {\n            \"channel\": \"system.selection.file\",\n            \"payload\": {\"fileId\": \"{{item.id}}\", \"fileName\": \"{{item.name}}\"}\n          }\n        },\n        \"children\": [\n          {\n            \"type\": \"Padding\",\n            \"id\": \"fpad-{{item.id}}\",\n            \"props\": {\"padding\": 14},\n            \"children\": [\n              {\n                \"type\": \"Column\",\n                \"id\": \"fcol-{{item.id}}\",\n                \"props\": {\"crossAxisAlignment\": \"start\"},\n                \"children\": [\n                  {\"type\": \"Text\", \"id\": \"fname-{{item.id}}\", \"props\": {\"text\": \"{{item.name}}\", \"fontSize\": 15, \"fontWeight\": \"bold\"}},\n                  {\"type\": \"SizedBox\", \"id\": \"fsb-{{item.id}}\", \"props\": {\"height\": 4}},\n                  {\"type\": \"Text\", \"id\": \"fdesc-{{item.id}}\", \"props\": {\"text\": \"{{item.description}}\", \"fontSize\": 13, \"color\": \"grey\"}}\n                ]\n              }\n            ]\n          }\n        ]\n      },\n      {\"type\": \"SizedBox\", \"id\": \"fspacer-{{item.id}}\", \"props\": {\"height\": 8}}\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\nThis opens a new window on the right showing all files in **python_auto_project**. Each file card is tappable to select it. The list is fetched live from the `projectDocumentService` using the `findFileByLastModifiedDate` view scoped to your project ID."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":501,"cache_read_input_tokens":13938,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":501},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"38739666-6c6d-40af-a98f-aca49e1aa763","uuid":"10ec28b5-d57f-4495-b082-2c5a946ebf99"}
